name: RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats.trackId
description: The trackId property of the RTCOutboundRtpStreamStats dictionary indicates the id of the RTCSenderAudioTrackAttachmentStats or RTCSenderVideoTrackAttachmentStats object representing the MediaStreamTrack which is being sent on this stream.
